        <h2 class="blog-post-title">How is our approach different from others?</h2>
        <p>Other approaches (for example Hudson Robotics approach for gene assembly) focus on robotic automation solution for gene synthesis. Our solution focuses on ability to scale to microfluidic device in future that will allow to minimize consumption of reagents and prices for artificial genes.Other equipment is oriented on low price of artificial genes, we are oriented on low price of equipment + low price of artificial genes. Order from the third party company does not guarantee confidentiality when realizing important biotechnology projects. Only own equipment and own gene synthesis facility may guarantee confidentiality during R&D process and it will be possible with cheap gene synthesis equipment.</p>

